<lb n="0542c13" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title><note n="0542020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0542020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0542020"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>慢法經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0542c14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0542c15" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">西晉<note n="0542021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沙門＝三藏釋【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙門＝三藏釋【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542021"><lem wit="【大】">沙門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">三藏釋</rdg></app>法炬譯</byline>
<lb n="0542c16" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT17p0542c1601">佛<note n="0542022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">告＝語【三】，說【宮】</note><note n="0542022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告＝語【宋】【元】【明】，＝說【宮】</note><app n="0542022"><lem wit="【大】">告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">語</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">說</rdg></app>阿難。有人事佛<note n="0542023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以後便富貴＝已便有富貴不衰者【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以後便富貴＝已便有富貴不衰者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542023"><lem wit="【大】">以後便富貴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已便有富貴不衰者</rdg></app>有人事
<lb n="0542c17" ed="T"/>佛<note n="0542024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542024"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">之</rdg></app>後衰喪不利者。阿難<note n="0542025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（驚）＋問【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（驚）＋問【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542025"><lem wit="【大】">問</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">驚問</rdg></app>佛。云何俱事
<lb n="0542c18" ed="T"/>佛。衰利不同。何故得爾。佛語阿難。有人事
<lb n="0542c19" ed="T"/>佛。當求明師。得了了者。從受戒法。為除諸
<lb n="0542c20" ed="T"/>想。與經相應。精進奉行。不失<note n="0542026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">其＝法【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＝法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542026"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">法</rdg></app>教受者。不
<lb n="0542c21" ed="T"/>犯如毛髮者。是人不犯道禁。常為諸天善神。
<lb n="0542c22" ed="T"/><note n="0542027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（所）＋侍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（所）＋侍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542027"><lem wit="【大】">侍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">所侍</rdg></app>衛擁護。所向諧偶。財利百倍。眾人所敬。
<lb n="0542c23" ed="T"/>後當得佛。何況富<note n="0542028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利＋（耶）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利＋（耶）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542028"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">利耶</rdg></app>。如是人輩。事佛為真
<lb n="0542c24" ed="T"/>佛弟<note n="0542029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＋（也）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542029"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">子也</rdg></app>。又復有人事佛。不值明師。亦無經
<lb n="0542c25" ed="T"/>像。<note n="0542030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">又復不＝復無【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">又復不＝復無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542030"><lem wit="【大】">又復不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復無</rdg></app>禮敬。不知不解。強<note n="0542031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">教＝效【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">教＝效【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542031"><lem wit="【大】">教</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">效</rdg></app>人受法戒。
<lb n="0542c26" ed="T"/>無有至信。受戒之後。故復犯眾戒。心意<note n="0542032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蒙＝朦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蒙＝朦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542032"><lem wit="【大】">蒙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">朦</rdg></app>
<lb n="0542c27" ed="T"/>冥。猶豫<note n="0542033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（亦）＋不【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（亦）＋不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542033"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">亦不</rdg></app>肯讀經行道作福。乍信乍不信。
<lb n="0542c28" ed="T"/>復不能念齋日燒香燃燈作禮。故復瞋恚<note n="0542034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚾＝喚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚾＝喚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542034"><lem wit="【大】">嚾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">喚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0542c29" ed="T"/>呼罵詈。出入&CB00057;<note n="0542035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">咀＝詛【明】</note><app n="0542035"><lem wit="【大】">咀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">詛</rdg></app>。口初不合心。懷憎嫉。使
<pb n="0543a" id="T17.0739.0543a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0543a01" ed="T"/>人殺生。<note n="0543001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔眼〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔眼〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543001"><lem wit="【大】">眼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>見經像。無有禮敬之心。若其有
<lb n="0543a02" ed="T"/>經。趣掛著壁。或擲床席之上。或著故衣被弊
<lb n="0543a03" ed="T"/>篋器中。或以妻子小兒不淨手弄之。&CB00195;熏屋
<lb n="0543a04" ed="T"/>漏。不復瞻視。亦不燒香燃燈向之作禮。與
<lb n="0543a05" ed="T"/><note n="0543002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">外＝凡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">外＝凡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543002"><lem wit="【大】">外</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">凡</rdg></app>經書無異。善神離之。惡鬼得其便。隨逐
<lb n="0543a06" ed="T"/><note n="0543003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔不置〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不置〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543003"><lem wit="【大】">不置</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。因衰<note n="0543004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">病＝疾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">病＝疾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543004"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">疾</rdg></app>之。適得疾病。恐怖猶豫。自念
<lb n="0543a07" ed="T"/>言。我初事佛。云何故復疾病<note n="0543005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">也＝耶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也＝耶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543005"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">耶</rdg></app>。不能自信。
<lb n="0543a08" ed="T"/>呼使<note n="0543006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">至醫師醫＝巫媚之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至醫師醫＝巫媚之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543006"><lem wit="【大】">至醫師醫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">巫媚之</rdg></app>師卜問。解除鎮厭無益。遂便
<lb n="0543a09" ed="T"/>禱賽邪神。眾過遂增。妖魅惡鬼。屯守其門。遂
<lb n="0543a10" ed="T"/>便喪衰死亡。不離門戶。財產衰耗。家室病
<lb n="0543a11" ed="T"/>疾。更相注續。不離床席。命終<note n="0543007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔罪辜〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔罪辜〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543007"><lem wit="【大】">罪辜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。墮&CB00410;犁
<lb n="0543a12" ed="T"/>中。當被考治&CB00353;罰。無有歲數。是人但坐不能
<lb n="0543a13" ed="T"/>專一。志意猶豫。無所專據。不信佛法。故得其
<lb n="0543a14" ed="T"/>罪<note n="0543008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">殃＝凶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殃＝凶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543008"><lem wit="【大】">殃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">凶</rdg></app>。衰<note n="0543009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔耗〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔耗〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543009"><lem wit="【大】">耗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>如是。世間人不知佛法者。謂呼
<lb n="0543a15" ed="T"/>事佛令得殃衰。不知其人行自不正。違犯佛
<lb n="0543a16" ed="T"/>經戒。心<note n="0543010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">專行惡＝意【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">專行惡＝意【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543010"><lem wit="【大】">專行惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">意</rdg></app>。眾態具足。身自招之。無有
<lb n="0543a17" ed="T"/>與者。阿難聞之。<note n="0543011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便頭面＝便更頭腦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便頭面＝便更頭腦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543011"><lem wit="【大】">便頭面</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">便更頭腦</rdg></app>著地。為佛作禮。<note n="0543012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔歡喜奉行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔歡喜奉行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543012"><lem wit="【大】">歡
<lb n="0543a18" ed="T"/>喜奉行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。</p></div1>
